WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.500 --> 00:00:05.400
Brother Ye

2
00:00:06.900 --> 00:00:08.600
What my brother Chen did was wrong.

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:10.466
I apologize to you for him.

4
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:13.066
Sorry brother

5
00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:14.566
You forgive him

6
00:00:14.566 --> 00:00:16.366
Stop targeting him, okay?

7
00:00:16.966 --> 00:00:18.466
Mu Qianqian

8
00:00:19.066 --> 00:00:19.600
On the top floor.

9
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.266
Didn't you see everything on the big screen?

10
00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:25.600
He's easing his relationship with you and showing you affection

11
00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:27.800
While having an affair with another woman

12
00:00:29.366 --> 00:00:30.466
Oh, right.

13
00:00:31.166 --> 00:00:32.833
Didn't he say it directly?

14
00:00:32.933 --> 00:00:35.000
They use you as a tool

15
00:00:35.166 --> 00:00:37.100
Why are you still pleading for him?

16
00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:40.133
First brother, it was Li Ruolai who framed him

17
00:00:40.133 --> 00:00:41.966
That's not who I believe he is.

18
00:00:42.266 --> 00:00:45.200
Besides, his feelings for me are real

19
00:00:45.566 --> 00:00:48.766
He also said he would take me away when it was over

20
00:00:48.766 --> 00:00:51.900
Make you the happiest woman in the world

21
00:00:52.100 --> 00:00:53.033
Okay?

22
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:55.600
How many people has he said this to?

23
00:00:56.800 --> 00:01:00.600
Besides, you framed me for him

24
00:01:00.733 --> 00:01:03.500
I almost jumped into the Yellow River and couldn't even wash it

25
00:01:03.966 --> 00:01:06.966
And now you come to me on his behalf

